Class HomeScreen
    Function build (Building the UI)
        IF user clicks "Login" THEN
            Navigate to LoginScreen
        ENDIF
        IF user clicks "Register" THEN
            Navigate to RegisterScreen
        ENDIF
End Class

Start
|
Display "Login" button
|
Did user click "Login"? --> Yes --> Navigate to LoginScreen --> End
|     
No
|
Display "Register" button
|
Did user click "Register"? --> Yes --> Navigate to RegisterScreen --> End
|
No
|
End
